      <title>恢复英国通货膨胀将保持削减税率的谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-15/resurging-uk-inflation-will-keep-boe-cautious-on-cutting-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国通货膨胀率可能在一月份的10个月内达到了最高水平，持续的价格压力恢复了，这使得英格兰银行因急于削减利率而保持警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-15/resurging-uk-inflation-will-keep-boe-cautious-on-cutting-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Feb 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
